                     <h2>WHAT IS A FLAVOR EMULSION?</h2>
                     <p>Flavoring emulsions are made through high-shear processes where we minimize the droplets of the oils within our flavor oil and emulsifier mix, usually gum acacia. Through this process, we made the oils into highly concentrated, water-soluble flavors that are great for high-heat applications.</p>
