                              <li>Sorbet</li>
                              <li>Much, much, more!</li>
                           </ul>
                        <p>Flavoring emulsions are a great choice to use to flavor any foods that don’t require baking. Since flavor emulsions do not have alcohol, they are great for flavoring frostings, puddings, custards, and more. Our flavored emulsions are excellent for home bakers, chefs, manufacturers, and small businesses.</p>
